  "system": {
    "biography": "<p><strong>The handler.</strong> A dwarf agent of DocWagon's <strong>Internal Security Division</strong> and Doctor Bob's old friend, who traced the leak to Expert Team Three. She recruits the team as Temporary Response Personnel, runs their 48-hour crash-course, checks in each afternoon for evidence, and arrives with ISD muscle to take the exposed mole away. She takes the job dead seriously — one wrong move blows DocWagon's security, the mole, and her career. Introduces herself at the Renton Clinic Citymaster with the counter-sign: \"Any of you need a shot of <em>Morphine</em>?\"</p>\n      <p><em>No published stat block (support NPC — attributes here are an estimate for a capable ISD field agent; GM's discretion). Appears throughout Malpractice (Missions p.33–45).</em></p>",
